{"tid":1472200,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢時既夢境。。。","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:00:20.000Z","uid":284419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b03ac94b5a067ba4a4bf65ae3048835b83f75d09","tid":1472200,"uid":284419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:24:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望可以成真</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：第一次開post唔知有冇開錯台，唔識排版唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日發夢夢見一位叫UN UN既絲打<br />\n8月18日係維園過生日&nbsp; 仲見到有300萬人上街一齊慶祝<br />\n<br />\n真係發夢都冇諗過佢生日正日會去遊行<br />\n因為佢初中生日曾經試過 無一個心目中完美生日會而喊<br />\n情人節無花收 唔開心<br />\n佢真係一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>非常重視節日</strong></span>既絲打<br />\n<br />\n邊有絲打唔係想正日生日扮下靚  著新衫 <br />\n過一日難忘生日？食餐靚飯 Post IG 呃下 LIKE？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我知道呢兩個月有好多巴絲都係黑衣中渡過</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夢裡面既佢，身穿兩個幾月既黑衫 黑褲 &nbsp;<br />\n成頭汗 溶哂妝對住我講 : <br />\n今年生日願望<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n仲話想收到一份特別禮物 <br />\n大家路過警總大大力鬧醒啲Popo <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔洗出手 </span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">淨係用你地把口大大聲咁屌柒佢地！</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知個夢真定假，當日我會買個蛋糕比佢係維園切，希望大家路見UN UN同佢講聲生日快樂。<br />\n<br />\n最後，呢個夢 真係好靚 300萬人上街 。<br />\n各位，幫UN UN實現呢個夢好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後最後，UN UN同我都好希望818遊行所有手足都平安返屋企，全民做一日和理非，好嗎？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oAFM6DJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoAFM6DJ.jpg&h=73a0ff80&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rkp2EYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkp2EYM.jpg&h=3a5741c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>8。18  <br />\n不分藍黃 自為黑白良心</em><br />\n<strong><em>徹底撤回修例<br />\n收回暴動定義<br />\n撤銷所有為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</em></strong>"},{"pid":"f8b19a58d6b01e8c17d6aed8f7fb546a92b5be54","tid":1472200,"uid":284419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:56:06.000Z","msg":"un un邀請8。18生日既一齊係維園切蛋糕再遊行"},{"pid":"ae429235d8a9a4721220905e6f271f113b9dc269","tid":1472200,"uid":284419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"黎陪下un un好嗎？"},{"pid":"42f48473c50f15a62af459ed7cb8121bbd17c42f","tid":1472200,"uid":284419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCy3pHw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCy3pHw.jpg&h=abe1d70f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uVpTAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uVpTAS.jpg&h=783ea8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umSopHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumSopHy.jpg&h=da7897ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2AUwny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2AUwny.jpg&h=a89e5fc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d9b074221cb38cdd404e10f3694a1cd5a0a6c8b","tid":1472200,"uid":284419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2YQUwnG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2YQUwnG.jpg&h=9c42617e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eir8APo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feir8APo.jpg&h=849fafe7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oatrnuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foatrnuq.jp